":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"去工廠做下"},{"pid":"26ff84a200eaa9f96efd20c779526159338aa90f","tid":1244423,"uid":33944,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:13:01.000Z","msg":"買2塊包 加啲照燒雞 加啲黃瓜 加啲汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c192e740c1168cf5a8a56569d238b5e2939aa0c6","tid":1244423,"uid":19858,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:29:54.000Z","msg":"7仔三文治唯一清泉"},{"pid":"6e4f66fbd7effc1c4b8767c9286f84f4f44eafe6","tid":1244423,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚正"},{"pid":"fcde582b6abbd205897014c935b5d8e6885f8b01","tid":1244423,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:32:44.000Z","msg":"其實佢既照燒雞真係唔似照燒雞味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd882dc383a737734fa7e00afcae040ed1a4c2fa","tid":1244423,"uid":113061,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:32:48.000Z","msg":"我都鍾意食呢款三文治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係我的做法 未必正宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n雞排<br />\n青瓜<br />\n白方包<br />\n麥方包<br />\n沙津醬 （唔肯定三文治入面係咩醬）<br />\n<br />\n醬汁：<br />\n醬油<br />\n鰹魚素<br />\n味碄<br />\n糖<br />\n<br />\n1）將雞排切筋，切平厚的地方，雞排厚度盡量平均<br />\n2）用以上的醬汁掩雞排半個鐘，煎熟，唔好煎太耐，肉會「鞋」<br />\n3）雞排切粒； 青瓜切片半圓，掩沙津醬<br />\n4）準備一面白方包，將雞粒，青瓜，沙津醬放上，再蓋上麥方包，完成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9800cddda309c67e26494d8d6fdf72065d20ab7e","tid":1244423,"uid":113061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd882dc383a737734fa7e00afcae040ed1a4c2fa","tid":1244423,"uid":113061,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:32:48.000Z","msg":"我都鍾意食呢款三文治<img src=